Lyrics - 

1
नौकरानी बना के रखल तू रानी के सपना देखाके 
ओला बोलाके चलनी हम ए राजा जी माइके 
पहिले जे जनती चूल्हा चौकी करवइबा 
नदिया किनार भेजी पानी भरवइबs 
त कबो ना बियाहवा रचइती आहो राजा 
माँगे ना सेनुरा टिकवइती 
आहो राजा कबो ना बियाहवा रचइती 

              antra 
हई साड़ी दिहल पापा जी के 
गाड़ी दिहल पापा जी के 
जवना पर घूमी तू ऐस करेलs 
कबहुँ खरच नाही कैश करेलs 

2.
कूल्ही कमइया सवत पर उरईब 
सारी सारी रात पिया ओनिए बितइब 
त आपन भोजन ना बसियइती 
आहो राजा मांगे ना सेनुरा टिकइति 

          antra 
कूलर फ्रीज़ पंखा टीवी 
संघे पइला सुनर बीवी 
तबो काहे ना पिया कदर करेल
हर घड़ी हमसे ग़दर करेल

3
जनती ना पवन पिया एतना सतइबा 
मेकअप सेकअप खातिर एतना रोवइब 
त प्रिंस ले ऑर्डर करवईती 
आहो राजा मांगे ना सेनुरा टिकवइती 
आहो राजा कबो ना बियाहवा रचइती

snippet.title: BISCUITS HALWA | Delicious Biscuit Recipe Cooking in Village | Sweet Halwa Recipe using Biscuits
snippet.description:
Today, in our village, we cook a halwa recipe using biscuits. Usually, halwa is made with wheat flour, but we use biscuits instead of any flour. This is a very easy snack recipe that everyone can easily cook in minutes.

We add milk, palm jaggery, and some nuts to make the halwa tastier and more traditional.

We taste the warm halwa on a rainy day evening! 

The taste is Delicious!

snippet.title: Phod-Cast Unleashed: Nyrraa Banerji's Shocking Revelations with Elvish Yadav!
snippet.description:
एल्विश यादव के Phod-Cast में आपका स्वागत है—जहां पॉडकास्ट को मिलता है एकदम देसी और तगड़ा ट्विस्ट! 🎙🔥

यहां सिर्फ बातें नहीं होतीं, बल्कि एल्विश के साथ आते हैं मजेदार रोस्ट, धमाकेदार गेम्स और सेलेब्रिटीज़ के चटपटे खुलासे। पहले एपिसोड में मिलिए नायरा बनर्जी से, जहां होंगे उनके सबसे बड़े राज़, अनकही बातें और हंसी के जोरदार पल।

कुछ ऐसा देखने के लिए तैयार हैं जो आपने पहले कभी नहीं देखा? अभी सब्सक्राइब करें और इस पागलपन का हिस्सा बनें! 💥 

Welcome to Phod-Cast with Elvish Yadav—where podcasts go wild and get savage! 🎙🔥 This isn’t your typical chat; Elvish flips the script with epic roasts, crazy games, and jaw-dropping secrets from your favorite stars.

Kicking things off with the fearless Nyrraa Banerji, we uncover her untold stories, shocking truths, and hilarious moments in an episode packed with unpredictability and Elvish’s signature swag.

Ready to experience podcasts like never before? Subscribe now and dive into the madness! 💥

#PhodCast #ElvishYadav #nyraabanerjee 

INSTAGRAM: https://www.instagram.com/phodcast.with.elvish?igsh=NnM1M3JzNjB1N3c=

Episode 4256: Dunkiwala Ko Kaise Pakde?
--------------------------------------------------------
Jethalal and his neighbours are increasingly worried as they struggle to trace Dunkiwala, the businessman who deceived Jethalal. Will they find a way to catch him?

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni
Episodes No - Ep 4256 | 30 Nov 2024
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sab #Latest #New #TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah2024 #tmkocfunnyepisodes #hindicomedy #comedyvideo #16yearsoftmkoc  #4000episodes

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

snippet.title: How British Left India? | The History You Wouldn’t Know! | Dhruv Rathee
snippet.description:
Discover the gripping tale of India’s final years under British rule and the turbulent path to independence in 1947. This video dives deep into the events leading up to partition, the power struggles between the Indian National Congress and the Muslim League, and the pivotal role of leaders like Nehru, Jinnah, and Gandhi. Explore how the 1946 elections reshaped India's political landscape, Jinnah's growing influence, the horrors of Direct Action Day, and the chaos of partition. Learn about the Cabinet Mission, Mountbatten’s plans, and the behind-the-scenes negotiations that determined the fate of millions. Join us as we uncover the untold stories, dark realities, and bittersweet legacy of India’s freedom struggle.

✅ Freedom At Midnight is streaming now on Sony LIV!
Click here to subscribe, starting at just Rs. 399 per month: https://www.sonyliv.com/subscription

snippet.title: AFTER SURGERY ZAIBA ഉമ്മയെ കണ്ടപ്പോൾ 🥺😓
snippet.description:
My sister meeting mom for the first time after the surgery. Mom was experiencing a severe stomach pain for past 1 month.due to that pain we consulted a doctor and we got to know that she was experiencing appendicitis and fibroids in uterus.we were really shocked and wanted to consult best doctor in the city. so we came up with a best doctor at ASTER MIMS hospital kottakal (Malapuram).and yah surgery has been successfully done.She has gone through 2 kindof surgeries one is laparoscopic appendectomy which is used to remove appendix and the other one is laparoscopic hysterectomy which is used to remove uterus through several small incisions in the abdomen. alhamdullilah my mom is doing great ryt now. i really wanted to thank dr shereef and dr ramya and the staffs who helped my mom in this critical condition.they treated my mom very well. I assure you that you will get 100% service from the doctors and other staffs from aster mims kottakal.they will look after everything and they will provide you with their best service.if we call them for any help they will be there for us in seconds. Alhamdullilah we r so happy and the surgery has been done successfully and my mom is healthy and happy.If you guys wanna get best hospital service i highly recommend aster mims kottakal.if you have any kind of health problems do contact aster mims kottakal(Malapuram)

snippet.title: NEW! Ep 4256 - Pakada gaya Danki wala !! | Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
snippet.description:
Click here to Subscribe to Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah Official Channel: https://www.youtube.com/taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah?sub_confirmation=1 

Click here to watch NEW Episode videos: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLPbh-P_C0BzSxhJ6UCi6tgujD-FsAy0sw

Click here to watch your favourite videos from Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah: 
https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLPbh-P_C0BzRYOkpGxKL-6QmvYSL_ZuCu

We bring to you the best videos from your favorite show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah. So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta', is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' and a mischievous son 'Tapu'. Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalal' to call his father 'Champaklal' from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

Cast:
---------
Dilip Joshi as Jethalal Champaklal Gada
Disha Vakani as Daya Jethalal Gada
Nitish Bhaluni / Raj Anadkat / Bhavya Gandhi as Tipendra Jethalal Gada (Tapu)

snippet.description:
Thankyou for the crazy response on Victory Anthem! Watch the official lyric video of this banger now and comment your favourite line!

#victoryanthem #khushitdt #lashcurry 

Credits:
Written & performed by- Khushi & Lashcurry
Prod.by - Audiocrackerr
Mix & Mastered by - Xolo

Lyrics:
Hook
Badi Baatcheet Industry Ke Logo Se
Poori Picture Bachi Abhi Promo Dekh
Mere Kisse Sunoge Toh Ro Doge 
Lashcurry Khushi Bakchodi Ni Dono Se
Bhali Bhaati Hume Roka Bhuto Ne 
Parivaar Khush Mujhe Tum Kya Hi Rokoge 
Bistar Bana Denge Noto Kea 
Agar Mehnat Ko Paiso Se Tologe

Khushi's Verse 
Rukegi Kalam Ni Jab Tak Hu Zinda Main
Marungi Tab Tak Ni Kala Hai Zindaa
Mujhe Lagta Hai Jaanti Sab Hu Main

Main Sunti Hu Logo Ko Jyada Ni
Par Haa Main Jaanti Sabke Hu Dil Ka
Mere Hote Padosi Ameer Jo Paisa Yaha 
Baatein Banane Se Milta..

Lo Aadat Daal Main Ruku Ye Hoga Ni
Socha Ni Kisi Ni Karungi Sab...
Paiso Se Laakho Ka Bharungi Pet Mein
Mujhe Ni Kamanaa Bharne Ko Ghar 
Phele Bhi Bola Hai Maqsad Ni Hai Mera 
Kamana Paisa Ya Kamana Fame
Faraq Hai Mujhe Badalni Hai Duniya 
Aur Tumhe Badalne Hai Ghar

Karne Se Baatein Hojati Hai Taaza
Wo Yaadein Ki Kaise Kara Maine Shuru Tha Tab
Koi Ni Tha Mere Sath Mein Rone Ko
Aaiyne Mein Baitha Guru Tha Bass
Kehte The Log Tere Baski Ni Tha Mera 
Dil Bhi Naadan Tha Maanta Sach
Par Kuch Ni Hai Aisa Jo Tu Ni Karskti 
Ab Kehta Hai Aaiyna Kehte Hai Sab

Episode 4255: Dunkiwala Ko Kaise Pakde?
--------------------------------------------------------
Jethalal and his neighbours are increasingly worried as they struggle to trace Dunkiwala, the businessman who deceived Jethalal. Will they find a way to catch him?

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni
Episodes No - Ep 4255 | 29 Nov 2024
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sab #Latest #New #TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah2024 #tmkocfunnyepisodes #hindicomedy #comedyvideo #16yearsoftmkoc  #4000episodes

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

snippet.title: New Mahindra XEV 9e & BE 6e First Impressions | Gagan Choudhary
snippet.description:
Namaste, Mahindra just unveiled their two new electric-origin SUVs, XEV 9e and BE 6e. Both are based on their new INGLO platform and feature the most extensive battery pack and most powerful electric motors of an Indian-made electric Car. The indicative price of BE 6e is Rs 18.90 lakh Ex Showroom for base trim while as, the XEV 9e on the other hand cost Rs 21.90 lakh for base trim Ex-Showroom.  Here is an in-depth video of both XEV 9e and BE 6e. 

Timestamps:
00:00 Introduction
00:38 Mahindra BE 6e Exterior walkaround, including Key Fob, Wheels, Headlights, Tail, Boot Space, Front Trunk etc
09:20 Interiors of Mahindra BE 6e including Screens, Steering, Features, Sunroof, Seats, Space, HUD etc
25:40 Rear seat space and amenities on Mahindra BE 6e.
27:41 Mahindra XEV 9e Exterior walkaround, including Key Fob, Wheels, Headlights, Boot Space, Front Trunk
32:15 Interiors of Mahindra XEV 9e SUV including Screens, Steering, Features, Sunroof, Seats, Space, HUD etc
37:30 Rear seat space and amenities of XEV 9e
41:28 Conclusion

snippet.title: ब्रेड से बनाएं कुरकुरी मसालेदार करंजी-झटपट व आसान रेसिपी ।  Spicy Bread Karanji for Quick Breakfast
snippet.description:
चटपटी ब्रेड करंजी, खास तरह का ब्रेड पकौड़ा, जो मिनटों में बने, स्पेशल ब्रेकफास्ट. Spicy and Crispy Bread Karanji for Family Breakfast.
#breakfast #nashta #breadpakora 

Ingredients for Spicy Bread Karanji
For Stuffing
आलू - Potato - 2 no, boiled
नमक - Salt - 1/2 tsp
हरी मिर्च - Green chilli - 1/2 tsp, chopped
अदरक - Ginger - 1/2 tsp, grated
लाल मिर्च - Red chilli - 1/4 tsp, crushed
हल्दी - Turmeric powder - 1/4 tsp
अमचूर पाउडर - Dry mango powder - 1/4 tsp
गरम मसाला - Garam masala - 1/4 tsp
धनिया पाउडर - Coriander powder - 1/2 tsp
जीरा पाउडर - Cumin powder - 1/2 tsp, roasted
हरा धनिया - Coriander - 2 tbsp
For Batter
बेसन - Gram flour - 1/2  cup
चावल का आटा - Rice flour - 1/2 cup
नमक - Salt - 1/2 tsp
अजवाइन - Carom seeds - 1/2 tsp
लाल मिर्च - Red chilli - 1/2 tsp, crushed
हल्दी - Turmeric powder - 1/4 tsp
तिल - Sesame - 1 tsp
हरा धनिया - Coriander - 2 tbsp
बेकिंग सोडा - Baking soda - 1/4 tsp
ब्रेड - Bread - 6 no

snippet.title: Family Values That Ham Saath Saath Hain Taught Us | Salman Khan | Saif Ali khan | Karisma Kapoor
snippet.description:
Discover the timeless family values taught by Ham Saath Saath Hain! Watch the video to see how this iconic film celebrates love, unity, and togetherness within the family !!!

Credits - 
Movie Name - Hum Saath Saath Hain
Starring - Salman Khan, Sonali Bendre, Mohnish Bahl, Tabbu, Saif Ali Khan, Karishma Kapoor, Alok Nath, Reema Lagoo & Others
Director -  Sooraj R. Barjatya 

Hum Saath Saath Hain Synopsis - 
The trials and challenges of a joint family in India, whose parents are Ramkishen and second wife Mamta, and have three sons and a married daughter. The eldest son is handicapped since birth, and is from Ramkishen's first wife. Mamta, the second wife, hates him, and like Kaikeyi in Ramayana wants the estate and wealth in her sons' names. She and her daughter's father-in-law, scheme together, and have the eldest son, including his wife and child, thrown out of the house. Mamta and her sons are all set to control the finances and the estate - until she finds out that her very own sons do not approve of nor support her actions in throwing their step-brother out of the house.

Mangal को मिले ढेर सारे Compliments

 Watch more viodes from the show here: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLdMXQl51UbMjX6BwpnuG6rvMN9N77mtRg

-----
Mangal Lakshmi unfolds as a poignant narrative, delving into the profound connection shared between two sisters, Mangal and Lakshmi. Set against life's myriad experiences, the story chronicles Mangal's odyssey in search of the ideal match, a 'dulha', for her cherished sibling, Lakshmi. As the tale progresses, it gracefully illustrates the intricacies of love, the resilience required to overcome trials, and the unwavering resolve that propels Mangal forward on her quest. Through the lens of sisterhood's enduring bond and the inexorable force of destiny, the narrative unfurls a tapestry of emotions, ultimately celebrating the timeless allure of fate in uniting kindred spirits.

Star Cast: Deepika Singh, Shubham Dipta, Naman Shaw, Upadhyay Urvashi,Vipul Tyagi

 DG-IG Conference Moving capital for Prime Minister's visit. Modi will hold a rally in Bhubaneswar on 29th. On the same day, Modi will hold a two-hour meeting with MPs, leaders and officials at the BJP office. There the Minister and MLAs will give the performance report to the Prime Minister.

Sunn Mere Dil Episode 16 [Eng Sub] Digitally Presented by LUX - Happilac Paints and Ujooba Beauty Cream - Wahaj Ali - Maya Ali - 28th November 2024 - Har Pal Geo

Sunn Mera Dil Digitally Presented by LUX - Happilac Paints and Ujooba Beauty Cream

7th Sky Entertainment’s highly anticipated mega signature project, Sunn Mere Dil, is the most awaited drama serial. The mega drama boasts a star-studded cast led by Wahaj Ali and Maya Ali. Written by the renowned Khalil Ur Rehman Qamar and directed by the acclaimed Haseeb Hasan, Sunn Mere Dil promises to be a one-of-a-kind drama.

Sunn Mere Dil is a tale in which love finds a new meaning, where one person’s devotion quietly flourishes, often unnoticed. Their heart beats for someone who may never truly understand the depth of their feelings. Yet, in their silent sacrifices, they realize that true love is not about
possession but about selflessness.

Every unspoken gesture and unseen act of kindness brings them fulfillment, as they put their beloved’s happiness above their own, showing that love is not just about being together, it’s about redefining happiness, even at the expense of their contentment.

7th Sky Entertainment Presentation
Producers: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi
Director: Haseeb Hasan
Writer: Khalil Ur Rehman Qamar

Cast:

Wahaj Ali as Bilal Abdullah 
Maya Ali as Sadaf
Usama Khan as Ammar
Hira Mani as Hamsha
Amar Khan as Dania
Saba Hameed as Farzana
Syed Mohammed Ahmed as Namdaar
Shahvir Kadwani as Zaviyaar

snippet.title: Squid Game: Season 2 | Official Trailer | Netflix
snippet.description:
Let the new games begin.

Squid Game Season 2 arrives December 26.

Only on Netflix.

More Info on Squid Game Season 2:
Three years after winning Squid Game, Player 456 gave up going to the states and comes back with a new resolution in his mind. Gi-hun once again dives into the mysterious survival game, starting another life-or-death game with new participants gathered to win the prize of 45.6 billion won.

Director Hwang Dong-hyuk, who made history at the 74th Primetime Emmys® becoming the first Asian to win Outstanding Directing for a Drama Series, once again helms the series as director, writer, and producer. Lee Jung-jae, Lee Byung-hun, Wi Ha-jun, and Gong Yoo reprise their roles from Season 1 with an impeccable list of new cast members including Yim Si-wan, Kang Ha-neul, Park Gyu-young, Lee Jin-uk, Park Sung-hoon, Yang Dong-geun, Kang Ae-sim, Lee David, Choi Seung-hyun, Roh Jae-won, Jo Yu-ri, and Won Ji-an rounding out the ensemble of colorful characters in the new season.

Watch on Netflix: https://www.netflix.com/title/81203480

About Netflix:
Netflix is one of the world's leading entertainment services, with 283 million paid memberships in over 190 countries enjoying TV series, films and games across a wide variety of genres and languages. Members can play, pause and resume watching as much as they want, anytime, anywhere, and can change their plans at any time.

Squid Game: Season 2 | Official Trailer | Netflix
https://www.youtube.com/@Netflix

New players. New rules. After each round, every player gets to vote "O" to stay or "X" to leave — and a changed Gi-hun is determined to shake up the game.

Sunn Mere Dil Episode 17 Teaser - 28th November 2024 - Har Pal Geo

7th Sky Entertainment’s highly anticipated mega signature project, Sunn Mere Dil, is the most awaited drama serial. The mega drama boasts a star-studded cast led by Wahaj Ali and Maya Ali. Written by the renowned Khalil Ur Rehman Qamar and directed by the acclaimed Haseeb Hasan, Sunn Mere Dil promises to be a one-of-a-kind drama.

Sunn Mere Dil is a tale in which love finds a new meaning, where one person’s devotion quietly flourishes, often unnoticed. Their heart beats for someone who may never truly understand the depth of their feelings. Yet, in their silent sacrifices, they realize that true love is not about
possession but about selflessness.

Every unspoken gesture and unseen act of kindness brings them fulfillment, as they put their beloved’s happiness above their own, showing that love is not just about being together, it’s about redefining happiness, even at the expense of their contentment.

7th Sky Entertainment Presentation
Producers: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi

We bring to you the best videos from your favorite show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah. So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta', is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' and a mischievous son 'Tapu'. Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalal' to call his father 'Champaklal' from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

snippet.title: मेरा दिल तुम्हे पति स्वीकार नहीं करेगा | Charnon Ki Saugandh - Part 5 | Amrita Singh
snippet.description:
अपने गाँव लौटने के बाद, रवि को पता चलता है कि एक निरंकुश जमींदार द्वारा स्थानीय किसानों पर अत्याचार किया जा रहा है। वह फिर एक स्टैंड लेने और अत्याचारी के खिलाफ पंचायत चुनाव लड़ने का फैसला करता है।

After returning to his village, Ravi learns that the local farmers are being oppressed by a despotic landlord. He then decides to take a stand and contest the panchayat elections against the tyrant.

Star Cast - Mithun Chakraborty, Amrita Singh, Kader Khan, Prem Chopra, Asrani, Shakti Kapoor, Satyen Kappu
Director - K. Bapayya

Charnon Ki Saugandh (1988) Part -1 | Mithun Chakraborty, Amrita Singh | Blockbuster Action Movie

"Charnon Ki Saugandh" is a Bollywood movie released in 1988, featuring Mithun Chakraborty in the lead role. Directed by K. Bapaiah, the film falls into the action and drama genres. Here's a brief synopsis of the movie:

The film revolves around the character of Shiva (Mithun Chakraborty), who is a loyal and fearless servant to a wealthy and influential family. He is deeply devoted to the family's elderly matriarch, Thakurain (Nirupa Roy), and her grandson, Shakti (Amrish Puri).

Trouble brews in the household when a cunning and treacherous relative named Sher Singh (Prem Chopra) plots to seize the family's wealth and property. Sher Singh is determined to eliminate Shiva, who stands in his way as a loyal and protective figure.

Amidst a series of dramatic events, Shiva is framed for a crime he did not commit, leading to his arrest and imprisonment. However, his commitment to justice and loyalty to the family remain unwavering.

While in prison, Shiva faces numerous challenges and obstacles, but he never loses hope. He eventually manages to escape and returns to Thakurain's estate to expose Sher Singh's deceitful intentions and bring him to justice.

"Charnon Ki Saugandh" is a story of honor, loyalty, and the battle between good and evil. Mithun Chakraborty's performance as Shiva is a key highlight of the film, and it combines elements of action, drama, and suspense. The movie also explores themes of family values and the resilience of the human spirit in the face of adversity.

Sunn Mere Dil Episode 15 [Eng Sub] Digitally Presented by LUX - Happilac Paints and Ujooba Beauty Cream - Wahaj Ali - Maya Ali - 27th November 2024 - Har Pal Geo

Sunn Mera Dil Digitally Presented by LUX - Happilac Paints and Ujooba Beauty Cream

7th Sky Entertainment’s highly anticipated mega signature project, Sunn Mere Dil, is the most awaited drama serial. The mega drama boasts a star-studded cast led by Wahaj Ali and Maya Ali. Written by the renowned Khalil Ur Rehman Qamar and directed by the acclaimed Haseeb Hasan, Sunn Mere Dil promises to be a one-of-a-kind drama.

Sunn Mere Dil is a tale in which love finds a new meaning, where one person’s devotion quietly flourishes, often unnoticed. Their heart beats for someone who may never truly understand the depth of their feelings. Yet, in their silent sacrifices, they realize that true love is not about
possession but about selflessness.

Every unspoken gesture and unseen act of kindness brings them fulfillment, as they put their beloved’s happiness above their own, showing that love is not just about being together, it’s about redefining happiness, even at the expense of their contentment.

-----
Mangal Lakshmi unfolds as a poignant narrative, delving into the profound connection shared between two sisters, Mangal and Lakshmi. Set against life's myriad experiences, the story chronicles Mangal's odyssey in search of the ideal match, a 'dulha', for her cherished sibling, Lakshmi. As the tale progresses, it gracefully illustrates the intricacies of love, the resilience required to overcome trials, and the unwavering resolve that propels Mangal forward on her quest. Through the lens of sisterhood's enduring bond and the inexorable force of destiny, the narrative unfurls a tapestry of emotions, ultimately celebrating the timeless allure of fate in uniting kindred spirits.

Star Cast: Deepika Singh, Shubham Dipta, Naman Shaw, Upadhyay Urvashi,Vipul Tyagi

After the grand success of Gulabi Gaal, Voila Digi Private Limited brings to you 'Shaadi Kar Lenge'. Here's the teaser, full music video releasing on 28th November at 11am. Starring Bindass Kavya & Pravisht Mishra and sung / written / composed by Aniket Shukla, we hope you guys love this music video. #bindasskavya #pravishtmishra #aniketshukla #aniketshukla #shaadikarlenge #voiladigi
